test_even_range:
assert [4, 6] == [10, 12, 14, 16]
  At index 0 diff: 4 != 10
  Right contains 2 more items, first extra item: 14
  Full diff:
  - [10, 12, 14, 16]
  + [4, 6]
test_large_range:
assert [3, 4, 5, 6, 7] == [5, 6, 7, 8]
  At index 0 diff: 3 != 5
  Left contains one more item: 7
  Full diff:
  - [5, 6, 7, 8]
  + [3, 4, 5, 6, 7]
